  "text": "🚚 Food Truck Vendors Wanted for July 4th! 🇺🇸🎆\n\nThe City of LaBelle is bringing the Fourth of July celebration to Barron Park, and we are looking for food trucks to join us for an evening of live music, fireworks, and community fun!\n\nFood truck vendors interested in participating must apply through Eventeny and select July 4th as as your requested date.\n\nApply here: https://www.eventeny.com/events/vendor/?id=47497\n\nThank you!",
