{
  "facebookUrl": "https://www.facebook.com/groups/SWFLFoodTruckDepot",
  "text": "Hello friends, family, and amazing customers! 🌟\n\nWe are thrilled to officially announce that we are finally licensed and ready to roll! 🚚🔥\n\nA lot of people have been asking when we’ll be back, and we truly appreciate all the support, patience, and love you’ve shown us. We can’t wait to serve you all again very soon!\n\nRight now, we are searching for the perfect permanent spot, and as soon as we lock it in, we’ll let everyone know. In the meantime, we are open to suggestions! If there’s a place where you’d love to see us serving great lunches on weekends or dinners during the week, send us your ideas 📍Naples and Bonita spring for now🍔🌮🥪\n\nWe’re also working on some exciting NEW menu items that we can’t wait for you to try… so stay tuned 👀🔥\n\nThank you again for supporting our journey. We’ll be back very soon and better than ever! ❤️",
